### 4. Additional Notes

The **open** and **close** endpoints of the *globals* API allow opening and closing product actions based on **region**, **environment**, and **ecosystem**.
Product closure is handled during the **DPI precheck** phase.

> **Note:**
> Currently, only the **oracle_cluster** product can be opened or closed.
> For other products, a new `open/close product` call needs to be added in each **Rego** for all products.

